{290}{}{那你为什么要打断我！！利沃斯的某个白痴偷了它！说服他们回来，在抽屉里找到它，如果有帮助的话，你甚至可以开枪打死某人。但是给我找那本书！！ -- Why the hell are you interrupting me then!! Some idiot from Livos stole it! Talk them into returning, find it in some drawer, you can even shoot someone if that helps. But find me the book!!}
### {291}{999}{Okay, I'll go looking.}
{291}{999}{好的，我去看看。 -- Okay, I'll go looking.}


### {300}{}{[Ludwig practically rips the book from your hands] Yes! Yes!! Here it is!! Now I can continue my research! Take this, just as I promised [Ludwig gives you a piece of map]. And you can now have access to my best stock.}
{300}{}{[路德维希几乎把书从你手里撕了下来]是的！对给你！！现在我可以继续我的研究了！拿着这个，正如我承诺的那样[路德维希给你一张地图]。你现在可以使用我最好的股票了。 -- [Ludwig practically rips the book from your hands] Yes! Yes!! Here it is!! Now I can continue my research! Take this, just as I promised [Ludwig gives you a piece of map]. And you can now have access to my best stock.}
### {301}{031}{What is it? A map?}
{301}{031}{它是什么？地图？ -- What is it? A map?}


### {310}{}{Edward bought it. He thought it was some schematics, so he sold it to me eventually. Probably it's a piece of a map, showing how to get to the Renaissance, a city of wonders. I've heard that it has clean water, fresh air. A whole city untouched by the war! I wanted to find it myself when I was younger, but now I never will. If you do, remember your old friend, who gave this to you.}
{310}{}{爱德华买了它。他认为这是一些示意图，所以他最终把它卖给了我。也许这是一张地图，显示了如何到达文艺复兴时期，一个充满奇迹的城市。我听说这里有干净的水，新鲜的空气。一整座未受战争影响的城市！我年轻的时候就想自己找，但现在我再也找不到了。如果你这样做了，记得你的老朋友，他给了你这个。 -- Edward bought it. He thought it was some schematics, so he sold it to me eventually. Probably it's a piece of a map, showing how to get to the Renaissance, a city of wonders. I've heard that it has clean water, fresh air. A whole city untouched by the war! I wanted to find it myself when I was younger, but now I never will. If you do, remember your old friend, who gave this to you.}
### {311}{Barter}{Of course. And now show me what you have in stock.}
{311}{Barter}{当然现在给我看看你有什么存货。 -- Of course. And now show me what you have in stock.}
### {312}{999}{Thanks for the map. I'll come by later.}
{312}{999}{谢谢你的地图。我稍后再来。 -- Thanks for the map. I'll come by later.}

### {320}{}{I don't have time to leave Livos and chat with some vagabonds. I got out only once, to the Chamber of Commerce by the entrance. That was the time when I chose someone to marry. Edward gathered some girls for me and I picked the best one. Veronica, my current spouse.}
{320}{}{我没有时间离开利沃斯和一些流浪汉聊天。我只出过一次门，到了门口的商会。那是我选择结婚的时候。爱德华为我找了几个女孩，我挑选了最好的一个。维罗妮卡，我现在的配偶。 -- I don't have time to leave Livos and chat with some vagabonds. I got out only once, to the Chamber of Commerce by the entrance. That was the time when I chose someone to marry. Edward gathered some girls for me and I picked the best one. Veronica, my current spouse.}
### {321}{010}{I see. Another question then.}
{321}{010}{我明白了。那又是一个问题。 -- I see. Another question then.}


